{"tid":1528814,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"#Dunkirk2019 大嶼山大撤退絕對係香港史上重要既一役！","createTime":"2019-09-01T15:11:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-01T18:27:38.000Z","uid":82002,"like":124,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"16c0ba41e735045b71252309122dd3b6ae0f2e9f","tid":1528814,"uid":82002,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-01T15:11:22.000Z","msg":"每一個偉大既民族，<br />\n都有象徵住佢地民族精神既韌性，<br />\n都有一啲扣人心弦，定義呢個民族既歷史時刻。<br />\n1940年既敦克爾克，2019年既大嶼山<br />\n都係象徵住為左保衛自由世界，<br />\n同邪惡軸心奮力一戰既決心同意志。<br />\n<br />\n當年英國漁民用成千上萬架漁船同艇仔，<br />\n將三十萬英國士兵安全接回英吉利海峽；<br />\n今日香港人用潮水咁多既私家車，<br />\n將一個又一個義士從截斷交通，彈盡糧絕既大嶼山，<br />\n接曬番屋企！<br />\n<br />\n#Dunkirk2019，The Evacuation of Lantau<br />\n大嶼山大撤退，會係定義呢個民族既重要一役！<br />\n<br />\nWe shall go on to the end. <br />\nWe shall fight in France, <br />\nwe shall fight on the seas and oceans, <br />\nwe shall fight with growing confidence and growing strength in the air, <br />\nwe shall defend our island, whatever the cost may be. We shall fight on the beaches, <br />\nwe shall fight on the landing grounds, <br />\nwe shall fight in the fields and in the streets, <br />\nwe shall fight in the hills; <br />\nwe shall never surrender.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iA2qO4g.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiA2qO4g.jpg&h=16d2cd66&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4g2ipCG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4g2ipCG.jpg&h=75c1d2f9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tsc6yv3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ftsc6yv3.jpg&h=bcf7e7f8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/99NqO4w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F99NqO4w.jpg&h=8cd5544c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/TQuHRhT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FTQuHRhT.jpg&h=e4519811&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4b2a8